{"tid":2245463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門又加價 張俊傑數錢都數到攰","createTime":"2020-10-16T08:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T11:58:24.000Z","uid":38189,"like":40,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"01a191d485ed0bf70a70f6feddaa9357c677fafd","tid":2245463,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"我愛錢先吃饅頭繼續霸權<br />\n我扮下黃店偉大到死<br />\n這老闆喜愛賺錢到下世紀<br />\n請你別投訴將這五仁奉獻給你<br />\n<br />\n龍門憑甚麼　出信若未令你擊退<br />\n便宜地送出　寫在食譜的咖喱<br />\n頹飯六十蚊　要是你都可天天食<br />\n食肆的天才　煽動你加價<br />\n<br />\n龍門又加價張俊傑數錢都數到攰<br />\n來吧送給你淡口的奶茶和特制汁醬<br />\n如成日幫襯龍門拿幸福的光環<br />\n龍門焗豬意要收足八十貴貴貴貴那麼多<br />\n<br />\n將我手足經濟一一拋到銀行<br />\n誣衊侍應　律師信出埋了<br />\n香港之王是我"},{"pid":"4129e8c442bc8aadc09ae6c0bb962f57e7f20679","tid":2245463,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62d3b2ca4ad0436f4366aadc253ffd9ca047eb31","tid":2245463,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68b9fdf43a61659a7de0cf8780edc59d8d94963","tid":2245463,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd985ddc01ba8558372b827b00e87f362c971409","tid":2245463,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27702b8462c53e157d7dfc64170460314324916b","tid":2245463,"uid":38189,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4129e8c442bc8aadc09ae6c0bb962f57e7f20679","tid":2245463,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:53:41.000Z","msg":"樓主高產"},{"pid":"1395515a0c9534f0e4c14ce789cd6cac524e773c","tid":2245463,"uid":31